Package: logitux
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: solaar
Maintainer: gzzy.dev <gzzy.dev@gmail.com>
Description: Logitech device configuration for Linux
 Local web app for configuring Logitech devices.
 Bundles Node.js runtime — no external dependencies besides solaar.
 Starts Express on localhost:3001 and opens the browser.
